445
00:28:31,519 --> 00:28:33,200
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da ljudi stižu do toga, zar ne?

446
00:28:33,279 --> 00:28:34,799
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da smo to čuli više puta, zar ne?

447
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:39,359
